WindOnTheWater,com,is,a,mashup,of,data,from,real,time,public,wind,sensors,and,Google,Maps,It,was,built,as,a,resource,for,kiteboarding,windsurfing,sailing,and,other,wind,based,activities,WindOnTheWater,com,exposes,its,mashed,up,data,through,a,free,API,Through,simple,HTTP,calls,developers,can,automate,access,to,wind,data,tides,webcams,and,more,filterable,by,region,or,specified,location